			<td colspan="6" class="DetailTitle" style="text-align:center;">
                            Summary on Grant Application Form</td>
		</tr>
		<tr>
			<td colspan="6" class="DetailValue" style="padding:5px;">
                        <span id="lblAbstract">The purpose of this application is to install a series of cutting edge equipment facilities, to support multidisciplinary research into the physical, engineering and mathematical sciences in seven 5* departments at Oxford University in collaboration with academic, governmental and industrial research partners.  The equipment requested consists of a quantum squid magnetometer, femtosecond laser, atomic force microscope, scanning electron microscope, surface analysis equipment, device fabrication and assessment equipment, and computing facilities.  This equipment will be used to support a wide spectrum of research concentrated mainly on solid state physics and chemistry and associated engineering applications, including a new Multipurpose Surface Analysis Facility and a Centre for Advanced Terminal Technologies.</span>
                        </td>
		</tr>
